Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.89,0:00:02.51,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.51,0:00:06.06,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The fall days are very comfortable.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.06,0:00:08.35,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}How is your health?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.35,0:00:09.29,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,I am doing well.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.29,0:00:11.99,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Recently, there's been a change in my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.99,0:00:15.41,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,I have a new roommate in my cell.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:20.25,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure if he's pure evil or just a fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.25,0:00:21.74,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,One thing's for sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.74,0:00:27.83,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,He's the reason I'm able to continue writing letters to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.83,0:00:30.75,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,It won't be long before we are able to meet.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.75,0:00:35.75,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,I hope to tell you much about my roommate, my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.75,0:00:38.34,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,I eagerly anticipate the day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.34,0:00:39.01,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sincerely yours.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.94,0:02:14.90,On Screen,EpTitle,0000,0000,0000,,Everybody Loves Pajamas
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.65,0:02:24.39,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Gramps.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.39,0:02:25.76,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Where's your partner?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.76,0:02:28.15,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, he went to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.15,0:02:30.44,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,What? I told you to always get permission and
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.44,0:02:31.83,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,accompany him to the restroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.92,0:02:36.48,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, he's taking a dump, so I figured I shouldn't tag along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.48,0:02:37.64,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.64,0:02:40.20,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Shachi needed to take a dump, so he tagged along.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.20,0:02:42.18,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,That's not the issue here.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.18,0:02:44.73,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, now I need to take a dump.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.73,0:02:46.25,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Will you come with me, guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.25,0:02:47.21,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.68,0:02:50.85,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, if they find us,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.85,0:02:52.79,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,they won't even bother sending us to the disciplinary room.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.79,0:02:53.70,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.72,0:02:55.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I want to go to the warden's room,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.33,0:02:57.01,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,not the disciplinary room, Shake-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.03,0:02:58.10,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shachi.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.11,0:03:00.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to find proof that he's breaking the law.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:01.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you his pawn?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.57,0:03:02.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the way, Hamachi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.72,0:03:03.70,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.70,0:03:05.35,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's impossible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.35,0:03:09.06,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Do you realize how many locked doors we have to go through?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.06,0:03:10.21,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, this is Kamiya.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.85,0:03:12.96,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,What?! What are you doing, you idiot?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.23,0:03:15.96,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, did they find out that we ditched our work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.28,0:03:17.49,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,You lost the keys?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.49,0:03:18.96,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Were they stolen?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.55,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it wasn't us.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.55,0:03:23.75,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get back before we're caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.75,0:03:25.33,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Grow a spine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.33,0:03:27.90,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They're busy looking for whoever stole the keys.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.90,0:03:30.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They won't care about a couple fellows skipping work.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.02,0:03:30.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.74,0:03:33.51,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,They're gonna care!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.51,0:03:35.22,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Because the person who stole the keys is right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.22,0:03:36.02,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.02,0:03:37.98,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's you! Why are you acting surprised?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.41,0:03:40.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't steal anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.25,0:03:41.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I just picked up the keys after someone dropped them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.99,0:03:43.39,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And I'm going to give them back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.39,0:03:46.16,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't make it okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.16,0:03:49.03,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, you're going all the way this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.03,0:03:51.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, time for revenge, Itachi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.51,0:03:52.75,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,That's not even close to my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.39,0:03:56.64,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, let's disguise ourselves so we don't stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.64,0:03:57.94,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,You're the man, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.94,0:03:59.85,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,You must have stolen clothes from the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.94,0:04:01.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.85,0:04:03.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a guard in pajamas.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.24,0:04:05.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're the prisoner I'm bringing in.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.36,0:04:07.53,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing's changed!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.53,0:04:08.97,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,How are you a guard in pajamas?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.82,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,The only difference is you're wearing a western style prison uniform
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.82,0:04:11.51,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,instead of an Asian one!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.51,0:04:12.52,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't blame me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.72,0:04:15.55,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The guard was working a night shift so he had his pajamas on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.55,0:04:18.27,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why was the guard wearing pajamas like that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.27,0:04:20.84,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Hell, you might as well be naked!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.84,0:04:22.26,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.26,0:04:23.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If I put on a bandanna and carry a stick...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.85,0:04:27.35,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,See? Don't I look like a guard in pajamas?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.35,0:04:30.12,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Don't act like guards in pajamas are a common phenomenon!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.12,0:04:31.48,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Nobody's seen one before!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.48,0:04:32.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Then I won't pretend to be a guard.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.93,0:04:36.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a pajama kid with a pillow and I don't believe in ghosts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.40,0:04:39.02,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why would a pajama kid be walking around with a prisoner?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.02,0:04:40.71,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,And who cares if you believe in ghosts?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.71,0:04:42.97,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,What's that in your right hand?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.97,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,What are we supposed to say if they find us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:48.18,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What are you guys doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.44,0:04:51.07,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,Why is a prisoner here with a pajama kid?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:51.97,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.97,0:04:52.81,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.85,0:04:56.81,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,K-Keep it down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.81,0:04:59.73,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Or this pajama kid is gonna get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,H-Help me pajama!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.89,0:05:03.82,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:06.18,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,He's taken the pajama kid hostage so he can escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.18,0:05:08.57,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, why is this pajama kid even here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.68,0:05:11.71,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Shut up! Everyone wants to be a pajama kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.71,0:05:14.60,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you keep talking, these pajamas will be torn apart!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.60,0:05:16.33,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,Stop! Don't hurt the pajamas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.33,0:05:18.33,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you a bad guy now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.68,0:05:20.19,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your hands! Outta the way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.19,0:05:21.05,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Clear the path!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.05,0:05:22.09,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.09,0:05:25.01,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,If you follow me, you know what's gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.01,0:05:27.73,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,These white lines will be completely red!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.73,0:05:29.77,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,About face, then march!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.77,0:05:31.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Then go into the locker room and change into your pajamas!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.39,0:05:36.39,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me, if you button them wrong, you know what's gonna happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.39,0:05:37.54,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,G-Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.54,0:05:38.85,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.74,0:05:47.43,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,We're on high alert!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.43,0:05:48.82,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,Get the prisoners into their cells!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.33,0:05:51.45,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Were they really stolen?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.45,0:05:52.86,Main01,F,0000,0000,0000,,I-I'm sorry...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.86,0:05:54.08,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Apologizing isn't going to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:55.23,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Where's the warden?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.23,0:05:57.13,Main01,F,0000,0000,0000,,Well, he's out right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:57.14,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,They've been found out...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.14,0:05:58.33,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Damn, why now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.92,0:06:01.04,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.04,0:06:04.19,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,This is the warden speaking.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.19,0:06:05.09,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,The warden?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.26,0:06:09.09,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, I wanted everyone to gather in one place.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.42,0:06:10.59,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.59,0:06:11.55,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,You're not the warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.55,0:06:13.60,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,I'm the warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.89,0:06:17.10,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm not feeling well,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.10,0:06:19.85,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,so someone else is doing the talking for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.05,0:06:25.61,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,W-Warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.81,0:06:30.36,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to our land, guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.36,0:06:32.37,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Warden's Office
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.37,0:06:32.87,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,This is bad, Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.87,0:06:34.36,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,We need to hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.36,0:06:37.37,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! I can't find anything incriminating!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.96,0:06:38.74,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.74,0:06:40.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I had the kids on the outside do some research.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:44.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I gave them one of the letters the old man's been getting
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.41,0:06:46.63,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,and told them to check the address.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.88,0:06:49.56,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you bringing this up now, Bro?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:52.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,They went to the address to see his son.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.58,0:06:54.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But they didn't find him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.31,0:06:55.66,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,He wasn't there?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.66,0:06:56.39,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.98,0:06:59.12,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And it wasn't just the wrong address.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.12,0:07:02.40,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He's no longer in this world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.80,0:07:04.55,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,You mean...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.55,0:07:08.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,His son died ten years ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.99,0:07:10.15,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Of disease.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.50,0:07:15.91,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He's been writing letters to someone who will never get them.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.60,0:07:19.70,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That would explain why he never got any responses.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.29,0:07:25.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But at some point, he began to receive frequent replies.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.86,0:07:28.17,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,From someone who no longer existed...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.46,0:07:30.18,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Who was it?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.18,0:07:32.59,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Were those letters written by a ghost?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.86,0:07:38.56,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,Our positions have been reversed, warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.56,0:07:40.01,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.01,0:07:43.60,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,Looks like your own men hate you as much as the prisoners do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.27,0:07:47.32,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, if you don't come out,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.32,0:07:51.36,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,we'll take out all our stress on the warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.36,0:07:54.53,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,Watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.53,0:07:58.17,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,We're going to beat the warden to death!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.17,0:07:58.87,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.26,0:08:05.88,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Stop this nonsense. It's for your own good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.03,0:08:08.63,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, unlock that door.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.21,0:08:14.64,Main01,E,0000,0000,0000,,Did you say something, old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.46,0:08:19.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,For an old man who was stuck in prison for the rest of his life,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.72,0:08:23.14,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,his son was the only light in his dark world.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:26.57,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But it was an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.57,0:08:29.65,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There was no light.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.30,0:08:33.64,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But you couldn't take that away from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.07,0:08:37.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,When you're sitting behind bars, the whole world is an illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.74,0:08:40.15,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So he gave him what he could.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.94,0:08:47.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That would explain why they only made small talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.92,0:08:47.92,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,From your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.35,0:08:52.92,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.79,0:09:01.18,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Bastards, you think you can get away with touching my toys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.41,0:09:05.66,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sending you all to the disciplinary room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.99,0:09:15.05,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I never imagined that the sick and twisted warden was
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.05,0:09:16.64,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,doing this for the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.33,0:09:21.53,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,He pretended to be the old man's son to hide his death.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.06,0:09:25.32,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If the old man is allowed to see his son,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.32,0:09:27.29,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,these letters will have been for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.68,0:09:31.96,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's why he's been trying to get me to make trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.70,0:09:34.72,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,To get his clemency revoked.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.12,0:09:37.43,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Why would the warden do this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.43,0:09:38.30,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Beats me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:43.22,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,He probably doesn't know either.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.30,0:09:51.43,Main01,G,0000,0000,0000,,Attention, criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.49,0:09:54.41,Main01,G,0000,0000,0000,,Open the doors and release the guards at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.41,0:09:57.95,Main01,G,0000,0000,0000,,Or else you will all have your sentences increased!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.18,0:10:00.95,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,You're the ones who locked us up in here!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.24,0:10:03.95,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,We're just making ourselves comfortable!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.34,0:10:07.57,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Shit, they started a riot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.57,0:10:10.58,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The warden's wish came true in an unexpected way.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.08,0:10:13.78,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,The old man's clemency ain't happening now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:14.91,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,That doesn't matter!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.91,0:10:17.59,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Those guys aren't gonna let the warden live!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.59,0:10:18.73,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,The old man's in danger, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.73,0:10:19.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Can't have that.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.94,0:10:23.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If he dies, there won't be anyone to prove my innocence.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.73,0:10:26.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Besides , I finally found evidence of his evil.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.50,0:10:32.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I'll make him pay for the crime of fooling a weak old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.23,0:10:35.86,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Bro, was that your goal from the beginning?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.86,0:10:38.10,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the help.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:39.80,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Now hide.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.80,0:10:42.12,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you mess around any more, they'll hang you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.37,0:10:47.50,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, you were using me for your own petty reasons?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:50.25,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's my turn to use you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.96,0:10:54.00,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I don't give a damn about the old man or the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.00,0:10:59.09,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,But I can't let our sentences be extended because of one stupid warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.09,0:11:01.40,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'll act as a decoy and draw the attention of the guards.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.40,0:11:03.52,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Use that opening to deal with this riot.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.52,0:11:05.01,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, that's...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.01,0:11:07.98,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Go crazy and get some more time tacked onto your sentence.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.72,0:11:12.27,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can continue to have a blast in this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.58,0:11:13.86,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.91,0:11:16.16,Main01,H,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.16,0:11:17.11,Main01,H,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.35,0:11:18.61,Main01,H,0000,0000,0000,,Get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.91,0:11:21.86,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Catch me if you can.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.24,0:11:27.05,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,But it won't be easy to grab the sleeve of the king of criminals!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.05,0:11:28.12,Main01,H,0000,0000,0000,,Your sleeves were ripped off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.83,0:11:30.87,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I'm counting on you, Bro.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:34.25,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I got this, Buri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.25,0:11:36.13,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,It's Shachi!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.08,0:11:40.72,Main01,G,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! They used the commotion to run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.72,0:11:42.25,Main01,F,0000,0000,0000,,Shachi's men aren't around either!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.25,0:11:45.88,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! If the hostages escape, we'll be crushed!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.88,0:11:47.03,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,Find them!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.50,0:11:55.13,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Warden, a lot of men have been injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.40,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,We need to get them medical care.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.61,0:11:59.65,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, hang in there. Hey, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.41,0:12:02.90,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,The prisoners want me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.90,0:12:05.16,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I'll hold them here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.58,0:12:06.12,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.12,0:12:08.24,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,But you'll be...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.24,0:12:10.26,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Are you trying to get yourself killed?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.26,0:12:12.67,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Give this to the old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.67,0:12:14.92,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzunosuke Beri
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.00,0:12:14.92,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,It's the last letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.19,0:12:18.55,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,Found ya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.55,0:12:22.17,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, what are you all doing here?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.43,0:12:24.87,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Move it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.87,0:12:27.57,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't hurry, I'll throw you into the disciplinary room!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.57,0:12:29.70,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Warden! We'll be back with help as soon as we can!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.70,0:12:30.93,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Don't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.93,0:12:34.54,Main01,Guards,0000,0000,0000,,Warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.14,0:12:36.59,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.59,0:12:39.40,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize that this isn't a letter from your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.88,0:12:43.18,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,If you are reading this letter,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.18,0:12:45.96,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,it means that I have disappeared for one reason or another,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.96,0:12:49.37,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,and you are no longer receiving letters from your son.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.41,0:12:52.47,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,However, you don't need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.47,0:12:54.25,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Your son is doing fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.19,0:12:57.95,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,His work has taken him to another planet,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.95,0:13:00.42,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,so it's difficult for him to send letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.51,0:13:03.49,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,There is a lot of paperwork that has to be done
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.49,0:13:05.55,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,before you can receive mail from another planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.49,0:13:11.10,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I apologize that I was unable to continue delivering his letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.91,0:13:15.79,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure that you no longer remember,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.79,0:13:18.22,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,but when I was first assigned this position,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.22,0:13:19.98,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,I was a complete outsider.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.62,0:13:22.99,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,After causing trouble everywhere I went,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.99,0:13:26.76,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,my parents dumped me in prison.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.03,0:13:28.83,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,The hardened criminals weren't going
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.83,0:13:32.49,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,to listen to a clueless young fool,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.49,0:13:37.34,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,and the guards resented me for my connections.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.18,0:13:44.21,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I would often find myself going to the oldest prisoner, you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.48,0:13:46.34,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,The rules of the prison,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.34,0:13:49.00,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,methods for handling nasty prisoners,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.00,0:13:50.72,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,the way to strike underhanded deals,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.19,0:13:55.45,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,as well as the fact that the outside light was a ray of hope
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.45,0:13:57.92,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,for the prisoners in their dark cells...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.92,0:14:00.28,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I learned everything from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.43,0:14:03.78,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I can't say that I'm a respectable member of society.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.05,0:14:08.03,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I'm aware that I have nothing to be proud of.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.03,0:14:11.95,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,However, you're the reason I'm able to stand
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.95,0:14:14.52,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,on my own, unsightly legs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.54,0:14:18.56,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,All I could manage was to help deliver these letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.95,0:14:23.61,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,However, I would be happy to know that they gave you hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.77,0:14:27.93,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,There will be a significant delay before the next letter arrives,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.29,0:14:30.67,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,but please don't forget that there is
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.67,0:14:33.27,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,someone outside who is thinking of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.93,0:14:37.13,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Please remember that your son is not the only person
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.13,0:14:38.94,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,who cares about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.73,0:14:42.57,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,It was nice knowing you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.89,0:14:46.69,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,From the evil prison warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.69,0:14:49.14,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,We finally shut him up.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.14,0:14:51.70,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, we're not finished with you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.36,0:14:53.64,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,Excellent.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.64,0:14:56.21,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,It's your favorite place, the disciplinary room.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.20,0:14:57.71,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Disciplinary Room
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.21,0:14:58.49,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,This will make the perfect tomb.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.49,0:15:02.76,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,Time to pay you back for all the abuse.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:14.69,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I have something to tell you guys who are
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.69,0:15:16.47,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,never returning to society.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.47,0:15:19.29,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,When entering someone else's cell, knock first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.29,0:15:20.94,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's prison etiquette.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.94,0:15:23.62,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Especially when you're entering the disciplinary room.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.62,0:15:27.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,There might be a really violent criminal inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.74,0:15:30.03,Main01,All,0000,0000,0000,,Son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.20,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,B-Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.20,0:15:34.09,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.06,0:15:37.15,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,It's too early for you to die.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.15,0:15:40.04,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You haven't met your father yet, you stupid son.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.60,0:15:42.00,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Bastard...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.00,0:15:45.09,Main01,F,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! Have you forgotten what he did to us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.09,0:15:46.42,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't forgotten.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.42,0:15:48.06,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let me handle this.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.06,0:15:50.51,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You've blown off enough steam.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.51,0:15:53.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If you still need some exercise, I'll be happy to take you on.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.17,0:15:55.82,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Well, warden?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.82,0:15:57.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget your promise to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.97,0:16:00.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,If I make trouble, you'll set me free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.23,0:16:04.36,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Now, who's the most stressed out guy here?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.36,0:16:07.39,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Let's start the first Tournament of Stress!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.39,0:16:08.73,Main01,Prisoners,0000,0000,0000,,Bring it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.27,0:16:12.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome to my disciplinary room!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.71,0:16:14.74,Main01,F,0000,0000,0000,,Warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.32,0:16:16.74,Main01,F,0000,0000,0000,,Are you okay, Warden?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.08,0:16:20.25,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,What? I don't see any of the prisoners who were rioting.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.57,0:16:22.63,Main01,F,0000,0000,0000,,Over there! There's a prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:24.12,Main01,F,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he in a western uniform?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.12,0:16:25.13,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, stop!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.13,0:16:26.13,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Where are you going?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.47,0:16:27.38,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.14,0:16:29.42,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Warden!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.82,0:16:31.48,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Set him free.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.48,0:16:31.88,Main01,B,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.57,0:16:36.39,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,These prison walls can't contain him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.21,0:16:42.43,Main01,I,0000,0000,0000,,The prison's really calmed down.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.43,0:16:46.25,Main01,J,0000,0000,0000,,We got prison guards and prisoners sleeping next to each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.25,0:16:48.94,Main01,I,0000,0000,0000,,They all need to relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.32,0:16:53.21,Main01,J,0000,0000,0000,,Still, I'm surprised they haven't hanged us yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.21,0:16:54.63,Main01,I,0000,0000,0000,,That's the thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.63,0:16:56.74,Main01,I,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that we won't be punished.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.74,0:16:57.61,Main01,J,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.61,0:16:59.59,Main01,J,0000,0000,0000,,The warden isn't going to let us off.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.59,0:17:01.95,Main01,I,0000,0000,0000,,Didn't you hear? The warden...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.69,0:17:09.92,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you're going to shoulder the prisoners' crimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.01,0:17:16.45,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I knew that it was risky to play with prisoners
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.45,0:17:19.01,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,since there are people like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.02,0:17:21.64,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,What I did was nothing compared to your letter business.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.78,0:17:23.93,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You chose a kind illusion over harsh reality.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.48,0:17:28.48,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Since you made that choice,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.48,0:17:33.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,you're obligated to keep up the lie until the very end.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.44,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But you got scared
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.44,0:17:39.66,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,that he would eventually find out you were lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.66,0:17:43.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,So you gave up and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.80,0:17:47.08,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, the old man's being allowed to meet up with his son again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.41,0:17:51.46,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I no longer have the right to walk through this door.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.74,0:17:54.97,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You don't have the right to whine either.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.97,0:17:57.31,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You're supposed to be an evil warden.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.31,0:18:01.20,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Tell the old man the harsh truth and laugh in his face,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.20,0:18:03.83,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,or keep feeding him illusions until the day he dies.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:05.24,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,One or the other.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.24,0:18:07.46,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Make sure the old man knows your decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.46,0:18:10.73,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,And then I'll forgive you for throwing me in the slammer.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.42,0:18:16.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Or else, I'll send your head flying and go back to jail.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.93,0:18:21.74,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,If I'm an evil warden, you're a demon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.17,0:18:25.24,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,The old man never told me
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:29.38,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,that it was so hard to give prisoners hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.24,0:18:33.08,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know what I'm doing anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.80,0:18:38.99,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,True, you've been fooling the old man for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.99,0:18:43.39,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,You pretended to be his son and offered him false hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.75,0:18:48.47,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,But your feelings for the old man are no illusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.46,0:18:51.41,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Come on. It's time for the meeting.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.85,0:18:53.61,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, I no longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.84,0:18:56.37,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,No longer have the right to go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.37,0:18:57.74,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.06,0:19:03.22,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,I have a criminal who's been
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.22,0:19:06.25,Main01,,0000,0000,0000,,accused of falsifying documents and identity fraud!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.49,0:19:08.55,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay, get in here, maggot!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.55,0:19:10.41,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,The victim is waiting in the visiting room,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.41,0:19:12.69,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,you mother-licking insect!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.69,0:19:14.75,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You bastards...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:18.30,Main01,D,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, pajamas are the best.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.70,0:19:22.76,Main01,C,0000,0000,0000,,I don't see anything happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.23,0:19:31.23,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Warden, time for some of the best prison role playing of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.03,0:19:34.80,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up, you have ten minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.27,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Any longer and the chief will find out...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.27,0:19:38.26,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,I mean, you're not allowed to meet any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.26,0:19:39.65,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Got it?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.72,0:19:49.43,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Good grief.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.43,0:19:53.36,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,We have so many nasty-looking guards around now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.43,0:20:00.93,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that you quit your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.93,0:20:03.19,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have another job yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.64,0:20:06.31,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm searching still.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.39,0:20:09.19,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.76,0:20:16.60,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I wish you the best of luck.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.60,0:20:19.28,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Try not to get yourself called an evil warden again.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.34,0:20:22.49,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.80,0:20:29.45,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Guard, we're finished.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.45,0:20:31.06,Main01,Shachi,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Already?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.29,0:20:33.97,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.97,0:20:35.62,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,I've been...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.62,0:20:37.62,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.62,0:20:41.30,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,We were able to make small talk, just like always.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.34,0:20:44.80,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,That's all I need.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:49.31,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Old man, did you...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.61,0:20:51.13,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,I read the letter.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.13,0:20:54.43,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,It was better than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.43,0:20:58.40,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,But your handwriting is still ugly.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.82,0:21:04.82,On Screen,Caption,0000,0000,0000,,Kuzunosuke Beri
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.96,0:21:04.82,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Warden, I've always been writing letters to my son outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.35,0:21:11.53,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,A son who turned out to have a nasty personality,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.53,0:21:15.83,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,but that foolish son of mine is dedicated to his job.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:16.53,0:21:19.34,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,I'm glad I was able to see you today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.47,0:21:26.25,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,Will you continue to write?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.54,0:21:38.58,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I will.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.65,0:21:41.46,Main01,N,0000,0000,0000,,It's a promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.46,0:21:45.90,Main01,Warden,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, whoever breaks the promise gets sent to the disciplinary room.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.26,0:21:48.63,Main01,Gin,0000,0000,0000,,Ow!
