Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.67,0:23:32.37,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Next week at this time:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.37,0:23:33.39,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,Sket Dance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.39,0:23:34.89,Main01,A,0000,0000,0000,,For real?!
